{"tid":1984203,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你班黃絲唔撚爭氣，唔好到最後果日至話唔捨得","createTime":"2020-04-22T10:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T10:40:45.000Z","uid":280613,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"74234aa9e4fac1605662fcd9b8c842ceb68c8776","tid":1984203,"uid":280613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"又比紅媒笑，大家做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每月$58都慳？</span></span><br />\n講咩黃色經過圈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而家去黃店食，閒閒地都$50、60啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">講真報媒真係少睇左，但黃報而家只係得一份，咁都唔撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足們你地唔好到蘋果執果日至話要買番份支持下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pWT1yP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pWT1yP.png&h=b33198f0&s=